Gold leaf is applied artfully on the side, adding a touch of elegance. The top of the cake is embellished with pink and red roses, gold-painted spheres, a golden leaf-shaped decoration, and sprigs of baby's breath, enhancing its celebratory look.

fields.title: Baking with Love Since 1993
fields.description_1: For over three decades, OvenFresh has been the heart of our community, bringing families together with the aroma of freshly baked goods. What started as a small neighborhood bakery has grown into a beloved institution.
fields.description_2: Every morning before dawn, our master bakers begin the sacred ritual of creating bread, pastries, and cakes using time-honored techniques passed down through generations. We believe that great baking starts with great ingredients and ends with great care.
